{"tid":1385734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解和理非同武一齊做？","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:18:59.000Z","uid":264691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc9dbd73404a1d72d72dd2b53fa614c7a43fe0a","tid":1385734,"uid":264691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"其實點解和理非同勇武要係同一個地方？<br />\n<br />\n次次遊行集會都有咁多狗<br />\n根本係請君入甕<br />\n記住我地目標唔係打死狗<br />\n係五大訴求<br />\n唔好成日掛住覆桌泄憤<br />\n<br />\n每次有遊行集會<br />\n等班狗駐重兵<br />\n勇武就去其他地方衝<br />\n例如銅鑼灣遊行就去旺角<br />\n機場集會就去返銅鑼灣<br />\n等班狗唔知守邊到好<br />\n久以久之啲狗一定痴線<br />\n但係又冇得唔守<br />\n亦冇藉口唔批不反對通知<br />\n<br />\n和理非做煙幕<br />\n武做遊擊<br />\n<br />\n只要tg十幾廿個人<br />\n玩下封路咁已經有效<br />\n放完野就走<br />\nBe water my friend<br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆不督灰"},{"pid":"2f2b6bbc5aee52595116fc97b31bb2986043caf0","tid":1385734,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"a94c16cb26a97321ae88e493a036c6b6c5477628","tid":1385734,"uid":264691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc4d30462122a02f889d6eb5ec8ecaa225c16aaf","tid":1385734,"uid":290885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"你睇番前兩日銅鑼灣 佢唔理啲和理非就得<br />\n到時集中火力拉曬啲勇武仲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeb3ec3900914ce182edcb1e918414f9ba2ea98","tid":1385734,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc4d30462122a02f889d6eb5ec8ecaa225c16aaf","tid":1385734,"uid":290885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"你睇番前兩日銅鑼灣 佢唔理啲和理非就得<br />\n到時集中火力拉曬啲勇武仲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"係，200萬人、7.1到7.28，路上根本無咩狗<br />\n和理非(甚至佔路)佢都唔多理<br />\n專心等夜晚打勇武派"},{"pid":"2dbb360d958a047768e8836064ca81396f1cb469","tid":1385734,"uid":264691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:16:31.000Z","msg":"咁係因為係返同一個地方嘛<br />\n嗰日如果係旺角玩點會捉到"},{"pid":"f3f27b9893d6795b8f774be80f1eebd5b76c8c58","tid":1385734,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n<br />\n[警世] 用啱方法救藍絲老豆老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"}]}